title: Complex Hyperbolic Sine Function
description: CSINH calculates the hyperbolic sine of a complex number
name: CSINH

input.name: X
input.description: A complex number for which the hyperbolic sine is to be calculated.

output.name: CSINH
output.description: The complex hyperbolic sine of the input complex number.

return_value.description: The calculated complex hyperbolic sine value.

fields.name: re
fields.description: The real part of the complex hyperbolic sine.

fields.name: im
